\c 1
\p
\v 1 NGASHI MONPI TRAR. YE SHU MASHIKAE 'EG. YOG PODANG SKU TSABS  YIN. NGA'ENGA DANG NGIKONCHOGDANGSKYABGON. YE SHU MASHIKAE 'EDRANG PORGYUD TENGA JA'DANGTSOGS LA TE NARIN CANDAD PATHOB SA KHAN GUNLA'IYI GE BOBRI'D. 
\v 2 KONCHOGDANGNGA DANG NGIGTSO BOYE SHUSHES SHESRGYUD TEKHYO JA' GUNLATHUGS RJEDANG JHIDE MANG NEMANG NGATHOB SHIG
\v 3 NGA DANG NGIKONCHOGTHUGS THAD KHAN NIMI TSHEPHUD CES SIPHI'. KONCHOG GIHA LAS SHES SISHED DINGA DANG GUNLADGOS SDOMTSHANG MASAL LAZADS. NGA DANG GUNLATETSHANG MAKHONGSHE SHES PO'ITHOB TEYIN NOG. KHONG NGINGA DANG NGAKHONG RANG NGIBZANG PODANGHA LAS SHES SISPALRGYUD TE'BOD DAZADS
\v 4 TE GUN NIJAS DEKHONG NGINGA DANG GUNLAJAL CHADMACHEN MODANGRIN CANGUNSAL LAZADS. TEJAL CHAD GUN NI'JIGSTENINANG NGAYOD KHAN NI'DOD PANGAN PA GUN NETHAR CESDANGKONCHOG GISPYOD LAM MINANG NGAKHAG NENCUG GAZADS. 
\v 5 KONCHOG GITETSHANG MACHO'ZADPA SANGKHYO JA' GUN NIDAD PO'ENANG NGA'ANG'IKHYUDTSHANG MAKHYONG CES SIMABRTSON 'GRUSCHOS SHIG. KHYO JA'EDAD PADANG NYAM POSPYOD PABZANG PO. SPYOD PABZANG PODANG NYAM POKONCHOGTHUGS THAD KHAN GUNSHE SHES SIYON TAN
\v 6 KONCHOGTHUGS THAD KHAN GUNSHE SHES SIYON TANDANG NYAM PORANG SEMSCUN NYAN KHAN. RANG SEMSCUN NYAN KHANDANG NYAM POBZOD PA.
\v 7 TE TSOGS SIMI TSHEDANG NYAM POSPUNDANGSPUN MOGUNLALCHESPA. KHONG GUNLALCHESPADANG NYAM POTSHANG MA LAKHYAB CES SILCHESPAYONG DGOS CESYIN NOG. 
\v 8 TAKALTES'IKHYUDTSHANG MAKHYO JA'ENANG NGARGYAS YINCHA'D NATE BO'IKHYO JA' GUN NIMI TSHENGA DANG GUN NIGTSO BOYE SHU MASHIKAE SHE SHES SINANG NGAMANG NGABRAS BUSMIN KHANDANGPHAN THOGS CANRGYURCUG YIN
\v 9 YIN NA'ANGKALTESSU ZHIG GINANG NGATEKHYUD GUNMED NATE GUNRGYAL LACHOS TEMA THONG KHANDANGJA RATSOGSRIGYIN NOG. YANGKHO'ISNGUNLACHOS KHAN NISDIG PA GUN NEDAG CUG GAZAD KHAN BOBRJED TEYIN NOG. 
\v 10 TE BO'I PHI'KHYO JA'SPUNDANGSPUN MOGUN NA'ANGKONCHOG GI'BOD DAZAD KHANDANG' LDAMA ZAD KHAN GUN NITHRO NEYIN KHAN BOSTAN CES LABRTSON 'GRUSCHOS SHIG. TE ZUGCHO NAKHYO JA' GUNKONCHOG GIDAD PA'IKA NEMANEMI 'GYEL
\v 11 TE NENGA DANG GUN NIGTSO BOKONCHOGDANGSKYABGONZHUGS KHAN NIYE SHU MASHIKAE 'EMTHA' MED PA'ERGYAL SRID DINANG NGAZHUGS SHES LAKONCHOG GIKHYO JA' GUNLADGA' SUSCHO'ZAD YIN
\v 12 TE BO'I PHI'GJANKHYO JA' GUNLATESLAB BYA GUNHA GO TEKHYO JA'SLAB KHAN NITEBDEN BA GUN NI KASTAN PODUGS TEYIN NA'ANGNGA'EKHYO JA' GUNLA'ISLAB BYA GUNDUS RGYUNYID TUSKUL YIN. 
\v 13 NAMTSHAG PANGAGSON TE'LUS YIN. TE GUNYID TU'SKUL CES BONGA'E'OS PASAM MA RAG
\v 14 YIN NA'ANGNGAGYOGS PA'I'JIGSTEN NECHA DGOS SHES BONGARGYUS YOD. BCI' ZER NANGA DANG NGIGTSO BOYE SHU MASHIKAE 'ENGA'I BOMNGONCUG GAZADS
\v 15 NGASHI TESTING NE'ANGKHYO JA' GUN NI'ISLAB BYA GUNYID TU'BOR CES SIPHI'NGA'EBRTSON 'GRUSCHO'D
\v 16 NGA JA'E NGA DANG NGI GTSO BO YE SHU  MASHIKAE  WANG DANG NYAM PO YANG SKYAR LOGS TE SKYOD CES SI SKOR GUN SHAD ZA NE SKYON JAN RUNGS GUN MA CHO' YE SHU'I ZIR RJID NGA JA' RANG NGI MIG NE MJAL TE YIN PIN
\v 17 KONCHOGYAB BICHOGS NE MASHIKAE 'RTSIWADANGZIR RJIDSAL LAZADZA NENGA JA'ANGKHONGDANG NYAM PODAM PA'ERI KAYOD PIN. KONCHOG GITEZIR RJID BO'INANG NGANAM MKHA' NEKHONG NGISUNGS SKAD PO'
\v 18 EBO NI NGAE LCHESPA BUTSA IN. KABO NGA MANGSTE MANGPO THADAD. SUNGIN NGA JHA TSOR
\v 19 TEBOI JHASTE NGAJHA' GUNLA  LUNGS STONPA  GUNI GTSOBO  YESHUI  SKOR LA BRI KHAN GUN NI NANG NGA MANG NGA LOKHYEL RAG. YANG LUNGS STONPA  GUN NIBRI'ZAD KHAN GUNLAKHYO JHA GUNI SANG NGA MANGA NGA TANG GOS SHES INOG. CHIAZER NA KHYO JHA GUNI PHITE GUN NYIMA SHAR SHARTSHUG PA LAMUN GRIG GINANG NGA'ODLDANG SHANTSOGSYIN NOG. TE NEKHYO JA' GUN NISEMS SINANG NGANAM LANGS SISKAR CHEN MASHIKAE SHAR RAZAD YIN. 
\v 20 YIN NA'ANGSNGUNLAKHYO JA' GUNLA'I BOHA GO DGO SHES BOKHAG CANYIN NOG. DAM PA'ESUNG RABS SILUNG STAN NITSHIGSGCIG GA'ANG LUNGS STONPA ZHIG GIRANG NGISAM BANANG BZHINBRIS TEMAN NOG. 
\v 21 CHIAZER NA LUNG STAN NITSHIG SGCIG GA'ANG MISAM BA NEMANEMA YONG NGAYIN NOG. YIN NA'ANG  TAMPE 'E THUGSNYID RGYUDTE  LUNGS STONPA  GUNI KONCHOG GI JHALTA GUN SALTE INOG. 
\c 2
\p
\v 1 KA ZUGSNGUN MAYIS RA EL LIMIR RGYUD DINANG NGARDZUS MA'E LUNGS STONPA MANG POZHIGYOD PIN. TE TSOGS LAKHYO JA' GUN NICHOS TSHOGS SIPHRO'ANGRDZUS MA'ESLOB DPONMANG PORIGTHONG YIN. KA GUN NISANG WA'ENANG NGAKONCHOG GISKOR LARDZUS MA'ESLAB BYA GUNBTANG YIN. YANGRANG NGISPON POGTSO BO MASHIKAE 'ANGPHANG YINKA BO'IKHONG GUNKHONG RANG NGIKHRAG GIRINSHAL DENYO'ZAD TEYIN PIN. TELAS GUN NIJAS DEKHONG GUN NIKHONG RANG GUNGYOGS PAMED KHANCHA' CES BOBYUNGCUGS TEYIN NOG
\v 2 MIMANG POZHIG GITESLOB DPON GUN NISPYOD PANGAN PA'ELAM GUN NI KAGRUL TEBDEN BA'ELAM BOKHREL MEDZHIGRGYUR CUG YIN. 
\v 3 YANGTE GUN NINAB SEMS SINANG NGAMGOB SKORBTANGS TERUNGSCHOS MA GUNSHAD TEKHYO JA' GUN NIKA NEMI 'OS PEPHAN THOGSLEN YIN. YIN NA'ANGTE GUN NIPHI'DUS YUN RINGZHIG NECHAD PETHAG CHADPHOG KHANNANG BZHINCHAD PA BOKHONG GUN NINYE 'KHOR LA'KHOR YINYOD. YANGKHONG GUN NIPHI'KHRES STORCHA CES POGORMI CUG. 
\v 4 BCI' ZER NAKONCHOG GISDIG PA KHAN NI PHONG NYA  GUN NA'ANGPHUD DAMAZAD DAMUN NAG GIGTING ZAB MO'ILCAGS THAGSDANGBCINGS TE THRIMS  CAD DIJAGTSHAG PANYAL BA'INANG NGATAGS TEBOR RAZAD TEYIN NOG
\v 5 YANGSNGON MA'EPHOR RGYUD GUN NA'ANGPHUD DAMAZAD DAKONCHOG GAMA 'JIGS KHAN GUN NIPHI''JIGSTENI KACHU LOGKAL LAZADS. YIN NA'ANGLAMDRANG PO'ISKOR LACHOS SHAD KHANKHONG NGIJABS STOG PANO ADANGKHONG NGINANG MIBDUN BOSKYOB BAZADS. 
\v 6 KONCHOG GISO DOMDANGGA MO RARGYAL SANGAN PAGNYIS KOME'SRAGS TEGOG THAL LARGYURCUG GAZAD TEYONG CES CAN NIKONCHOG GAMA 'JIGS KHAN NIMI RGYAD GUN NI KABYUNG CES BOSPEZHIG GITSHOL LASAL LAZADS. 
\v 7 YANGSO DOM MIRGYAL SA'ITE THRIMS MED DIMI GUN NISPYOD PANGAN PA GUN NIJAS DE'U THUG DESEMSSKYOS TEYOD KHANDRANG POKONCHOG GIJABS STOG PALODZER KHAN BOSKYOB BAZADS
\v 8 TEMIDRANG PO BOTE GUN NISKYIL LADUGS TEJAG DANGKHONG GUN NINGAN PALAS GUN NISKOR GUNTHONG CESDANGTSHOR CES BO'IKHONG NGISEMSDRANG PO BO'KHRAG LUNGYONG NGAD PIN. 
\v 9 KALTESKONCHOG GITE ZUGZAD DAD NA. KHONG NGIKHONGTHUGS THADCUG KHAN GUNTSHOD LTA GUN NEKA ZUG GISKYOBS TEBOR CESYANGMINGAN GUNTHAG CHAD DIJAGTSHUG PACHAD MED LACHAD PAKAL YINBOR CES GUNKHONG NGIKHYEN NAZAD DA NOG. 
\v 10 KHAG CHE'CHOS TEKONCHOG GI'DOD PANGAN PA'ELAM MI KAGRUL KHANYANGWANGYOD KHAN GUNLARTSIS MEDCHO KHAN GUNLACHAD PASAL LAZAD YIN. 'I GUNRANG GYAL CANDANGPHO SO CANYONG NGA NOG. YANGZIR RJID CAN GUN NISKOR LASPE RASROKPOZER CES LATSHAB SAMA NOG
\v 11 KONCHOG GI PHONG NYA  GUNWANGDANGSTOBS SINANG NGATERDZUS MA'ESLOB DPON GUN NISANGDRAG POYOD NA'ANG. KONCHOG GIDUNLAKHONG GUN NI'ANGTE GUN NISKOR LASPE RASROK POMO L LAZAD DAMI 'DUG
\v 12 'IRDZUS MA'ESLOB DPON GUNTENAG TSHOGS SISAM BAMA BTANG NGALASCHO KHAN NISEMS CAN GUNTSOGSYIN NOG. KA GUNZUMS TEKHRES STORCHO CES SIPHI'SKYES TEYIN. YANGHA MA GO KHAN GUN NISKOR LA'ANGKHRIL DGODBTANG KHAN GUNNAG TSHOGS SISEMS CAN GUNDANGTSOGS LASHI' NOG. 
\v 13 'I GUNLARANG NGILASNGAN PA'EBRAS BUNGAN PATHOB YIN. 'I GUNNYI MADKAR MO'LAS NGANCHO CES LATHAD DA NOG. YANGKHONG GUNKHYO JA' GUN NIPHRO'KHREL MEDDANGRUS BRUDRIGYIN NOG. KA GUN NIKHYO JA' GUNDANG NYAM POYE SHUGRONG SHES POYID TUCHO YINDANGKHAR JIZAZA NE'ANGLASNGAN PA GUNCHO CES SINANG NGA'ANGTHAD POCHO' NOG. 
\v 14 'I GUN NIDUS RGYUN LASDREL  LIPHI'LTA' NOGYANGSDIG PAMA CHO'MANE'DUG NYAN NAMA NOG. 'I GUNLADAD PANYU NGUN CAN GUNSDIG PA'EMGOB SKOR RINANG NGAKHYONG CES POSHES SA NOG. KHONG GUNNABS SEMS SINANG NGAMKHAS PAYIN NOG. KHONG GUNRNGANPHOG KHAN NIPHOR RGYUDYIN NOG
\v 15 'IRDZUS MA'ESLOB DPON GUN NILAMDRANG PO GUNPHANGS TESNGON MA'IDUS LABE OR RIBU TSHA LUNGS STONPA SDIG CANBAL LA. AMA MILAMNGAN PA'ERGYAB NEGRUL TEYIN NOG. KA BO'IPE NE'THADPA SANGLASNGAN PACHO'D PIN. 
\v 16 YIN NA'ANGKONCHOG GIKHYUD DITEJAG GASPE RAZERMI SHES KHAN NIBUNG BUZHIG GISPE RABTANG NYAN TEKHO'ILASNGAN GUN NIPHI'KHO'KHA'SKYES TE. KHO'SAM BAMED KHAN NILAS CES NEGAGS. 
\v 17 'IRDZUS MA'ESLOB DPON GUNNICHUMED KHAN NICHU MIGDANGLUNG RAGDRAG PO'EMA MUNDED DEKHYER RATSOGSYIN. TE GUN NIPHI'MUN NAG GIBTSON KHANG GUN'DAMS TEYOD. 
\v 18 'IMI GUNMAPHO SO CANDANG. TON MED DISPE RABAD KHANYIN NOG. NYE THUB ZHIGSDIG PA'ILASNGAN GUNPHANGS TEDAD PA'INANG NGAYONG KHAN NIMI GUNLAKHONG GUN NIGZUGS PO'I'DOD PANGAN PANANG BZHINCHO CES LATSHOD LTA'ENANG NGABTANG 'DUG. 
\v 19 'IMI GUN NIGJAN MA GUNLARANG THADCHO CES SIRANG WANGBTANG YINZER TEKHA CHAD RUGYIN NA'ANGKHONG RANG GUNNGAN PA'ETSHE G. YOGRGYUR TE'DUG. BCI' ZER NACI ZHIG GIMI'I KAWANG SRUL NATEMI BOTE BO'ITSHE G. YOG GARGYUR RA NOG. 
\v 20 KALTESNGA DANG NGIGTSO BODANGSKYABGON. YE SHU MASHIKAE SHES SHES PA'I'I'JIGSTENILASNGAN GUN NETHAR KHAN NIMI GUNYANG SKYARSDIG PA'KHRIL TEKHONG GUN NI KAWANGSRUL CUG GAD NATE GUN NINAS LUGS POSNGUN NISANGMANG NGATHU' CHEN. 
\v 21 TE GUN NIDRANG POMI TSHEPHUD CES SILAMKA BOKHONG GUNLABTANG KHAN NIDAM PA'EBKA' RGYAYIN PINTE BOHA GO TESTING NERGYAB LOGCHO'ESANGTELAM BOMANERGYUSMA SONG PIN NAGYAL LAYOD 'GRO. 
\v 22 KHONG GUN NIPHI'TA'IGTAM SPE. E BOKHROD DA NOG. KHYI ZHIGRANG NGISKYUGS PA'IDUNLALOGS TEZA' LACHA NOG. YANGPHAG BO THUS  TESTING NEYANG SKYAR'DAM PALAG GINANG NGA'GRES SA LALOGS TECHA' NOG.  
\c 3
\p
\v 1 NGAE LCHESPE SPUN GUN. 'I BONGA'EKHYO JA' GUNLA YIGE NYIS PA BO YIN. NGAE YIGE NYIS KA KHYOJA GUNIS NGON LA SLOBSTE YODKHANI LAB JYA GUN IDTU SKUL CHES TANG YANGTE GUNNI KA SAMBA TAN-TAN TANG CHES SI PHIA DRID.
\v 2 KHYO JA' GUN NI SNUN MA EDAM PA'E LUNGS STONPA  GUN NIMOL KHAN GUNDANGYE SHU'I SKU TSABS   GUNRGYUD TENGA DANG NGIGTSO BODANGSKYABGONYE SHU'IBKA'SAL KHAN GUNYID TU'BOR DGOS SHES BONGA'E'DOD PAYIN.
\v 3 TSHANG MA'ISANGSNGON LAKHYO JA' GUNLA'I BOHA GO DGOS. MTHA' MA'EDUS LASDIG PA'I'DOD PANANG BZHINRANG NGIMI TSHEPHUD KHAN NIMI RIGYONGS TEKHYO JA' GUN NIDAD PA'I KAKHRIL DGODBTANG YIN.
\v 4 KHONG GUN NI  MASHIKAE LOGS TESKYOD CES SIJAL CHAD POKA RUSONG YANG NGA JA'EPHA MES PO GUNSHITSHAR PA NEPHAR LADAG SATSHAG PA'I'JIGSTENITSHIR GUNTE NAZUG GAGRUL 'DUGKA ZUGGO MACHAGSZA NEYOD PIN ZER YIN.
\v 5 KHONG GUN NIMING NA'ANG'I GUNLANANG MEDCHOS TEYIN NOG. KA BODUSMANG POZHIG GISNGON LAKONCHOG GIBKA'NANG BZHIN LANAM MKHA' BOCHO'ZAD TESA BZHI BOCHU'ITHRO NEPHI LOG GAPHING NGAZAD TETE BO'CHU'I'KHORCUG GAZAD KYAG.
\v 6 YANGKONCHOG GIJABS STOG PANO A'IDUS LAKONCHOG GIBKA'NANG BZHINCHU LOG GIJAS DETE DUS SI'JIGSTEN PA GUNMED KHANSONG TEYIN PIN.
\v 7 'I NA DANG TSOGS LA KONCHOG GI BKA'NANG BZHIN LATE NANAM MKHA'EBAR NANGDANGSAGNYIS KOME'ENANG NGASRAG CES LALUS SHUG GAZAD TEYIN NOG. YANGTE GUNTE TETSHUG PATHEN TEBOR RAZAD TEYIN NOGNAM TSHAG PA'I'JIGSTENIDAD PAMED KHAN NIMI GUNLAKHONG NGISHAGSCHAD TEMED KHANCHO'MI ZAD.
\v 8 YIN NA'ANGNGA'EGCES PA'ISPUN GUN. 'ISPE RA BOMANEMA BRJED SHIG. GTSO BOKONCHOG GISKUN DUNLAJAGGCIG PONILOSTONG GCIGYANGLOSTONG GCIG PONIJAGGCIGDANG'DRAN DRAYIN NOG.
\v 9 MIKHA CIG GIGTSO BOKHONG RANGLOGS TEPHEB CES SIJAL CHAD POGOR TEYIN NOGSAM 'DUG. YIN NA'ANGDNGOS PO'KHONGGOR TEMAN NOG. BCI' ZER NAKHONG NGIKHYO JA' GUN NIPHI'BZOD PAZAD TEYIN NOG. KHONG NGISU ZHIG GA'ANGMED KHANCHO'MA ZAD DAMITSHANG MA'E'GYOD PACHO CES SI'DOD PAZAD DA NOG.
\v 10 YIN NA'ANGGTSO BOYE SHU MASHIKAE LOGS TEPHEBS CES SIJAG PONISANG WA'ENANG NGARKUN MATSOGS LAPHEBS YIN. TEJAG GANAM MKHA'EBAR NANG BOMAKU CODRAG PODANG NYAM POMED KHANCHEN. YANGNAM MKHA'ENANG NGAYOD KHANTSHANG MATSHADGRAG PO'IBZHU DECHEN. YANGSA ZHI KAYOD KHANTSHANG MATSHIG DEMED KHANCHEN.
\v 11 TES'ITSHANG MAMED KHANCHA'D NAKHYO JA' GUN NIMI TSHE BOKA ZUG GAPHUD DGOS. KONCHOG GIJAG PO'SRUNG TEGYOGS PASLEB CUG CES LABRTSON 'GRUSCHO YINKHYO JA' GUN NIMI TSHE BOKONCHOGTHUGS THAD CESDANGDAM PAZHIGPHUD DGOS SHESYIN NOG.
\v 12 TE JAGA NAM KHAE BAR NANG MET SHIG DE YANG TENEANG NGA YOD KHAN TSANG MA JHU TE MEDKHAN CHEN.
\v 13 YIN NA'ANGNGA DANG GUNKONCHOG GIJAL CHADNANG BZHIN LANAM MKHA'SO MAZHIGDANGSA ZHISO MAZHIG GIPHI'SRUNGS TE'DUG YIN. KA BODRANG PO'ILAM MI KAGRUL KHAN GUNNIKHANG PAYIN NOG.
\v 14 TE BO'I PHI'NGA'EGCES PA'ISPUN GUN. KHYO JA' GUN'ITSHANG MABYUNG CES SIPHI'SRUNGS TEYODZA NERANG DANG RANGKONCHOG GISKUN DUNLARTSANG MADANGSKYONMED KHANDANG JHIDE DANG NYAM POMI TSHEPHUD KHANZHIGSTANTHUB CES SIPHI'MABRTSON 'GRUS SHIG.
\v 15 YANGKONCHOG GIBZOD SEMSDANG NYAM PONGA DANG GUNLATHAR PATHOB CES SISKABSSAL LAZAD KHAN BOHA GODGO SHES POMA KHAG CANZHIGYIN NOG. NGA DANG NGIGCES PA'ISPUNPA 'U LU'INGAKONCHOG GISAL LAZAD KHAN NISHES RABSNANG BZHIN LAKHYO JA' GUNLABRI'ZAD TEYIN NOG.
\v 16 KHONG NGIRANG NGIPHYAG BRISTSHANG MA'INANG NGA'I NADANGTSOGS SIGOR RGYAN GUN NISKOR LABRI'ZAD TE'DUG. KHONG NGIPHYAG BRISKHA CIG GINANG NGAHA GO CES LAMAKAGS POCHA KHAN NISLAB BYARIG GA'ANGYOD TEYIN NOG. YANGSAM BAMED KHANDANGSTAN BZHIMED KHAN NIMIKHA CIG GIPA 'U LU'IPHYAG BRIS GUN NITON TAG BOMING NA'ANGRGYUR TEYIN NOG. KA ZUGKHONG GUN NIGJANDAM PA'ESUNG RABS GUNLACHO'D. KA BO'IRANG NGIPHI'NOD SKYALKHYONG 'DUG.
\v 17 DUSSLEB BISANGSNGON LANGA'EKHYU JA' GUNLASPANGPHUD DAD.  THRIMS  MED DIMI GUN NIMGOB SKOR RINANG NGAYONGS TEKHYO JA'RANGDAD PA'ENANG NGASTAN POMED KHANMI RGYUR CES LASHANGCHOS TE'DUG SHIG.
\v 18 MATSHAD PA'ENGA DANG NGIGTSO BODANGSKYABGONYE SHU MASHIKAE 'ETHUGS RJEDANGSHE SHES SIYON TAN NINANG NGAYAR GYASCHO YINSONG SHIG. YANGKHONG NGADAG SADANGDUS RGYUNTSHAG PASTOD PABYUNG SHIG. A MEN. 
